    • Content

      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all

cd E:/

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000
drop if winpc==0

drop if winpc_r==. | bet==. 
drop if failrate==. | winvalue==.  
drop if sdwin==. | shistakes==. 
drop if slostakes==. | swealth==. 
drop if gender==. | age==. 
drop if BMI==. |  malay==. 
drop if internationalstudent==. |  weekinc_2==. 
drop if wealth_1==. | wealth_2==.  
drop if perfuni==. | earnings==.  
drop if totalprpayout==. |  lefthand==.  
drop if smoke==. | englishspeaker==.   
drop if experiment==. |  mum_school==.  
drop if dad_school==. |  dad_qual==.   
drop if dad_hiqual==. | SBI_reminisce==.  
drop if SBI_anticipate==. | SBI_moment==.   
drop if opt04==. | opt06==.  
drop if depression==. | alcohol_dummy==.  
drop if happy==. | luckyans==.  
drop if bettingjust==. | vegi==.  
drop if risk==. | self_esteem_composite==.  

program define OET_ML1
args lnf sigma gamma alpha
tempvar j
gen double `j'=winpc^`gamma'/((winpc^`gamma'+(1-winpc)^`gamma'))^(`alpha')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end
ml model lf OET_ML1 (sigma:ps=) (gamma1:)(alpha1:)
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
estimates store m1

program define OET_ML2
args lnf sigma gamma
tempvar j
gen double `j'=winpc^`gamma'/((winpc^`gamma'+(1-winpc)^`gamma'))^(1/`gamma')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end
ml model lf OET_ML2 (sigma:ps=) (gamma2:)
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
estimates store m4


program define OET_ML3
args lnf sigma gamma alpha
tempvar j
gen double `j'=`alpha'*winpc^`gamma'/((`alpha'*winpc^`gamma'+(1-winpc)^`gamma'))
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end
ml model lf OET_ML3 (sigma:ps=) (gamma3:)(alpha3:)
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
estimates store m2


program define OET_ML4
args lnf sigma alpha beta
tempvar j
gen double `j'=exp(-`beta'*(-ln(winpc))^`alpha')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end
ml model lf OET_ML4 (sigma:ps=) (alpha4:) (beta4:)
ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
estimates store m3, title (Spec 1-a)




esttab m1 m2 m3 m4 using model4result.tex, cells("b(star fmt(3)) se") legend  title(MLE result)  nogaps compress replace
